		<!-- message -->
		<div>If you are using SIDLWIDL then changing the colors and attributes of the guage is simple<br />
<br />
The colors are split into RBG-  (red blue green)<br />
the higher you set a particular color, the more saturation you get.  It's kinda like mixing paint....more or less.<br />
<br />
If you look at the bottom section on the right, you'll see a template section that has the guage info in there.  Expand it to view the different options.<br />
<br />
Best advice is to just play with it till ya see what does what.  Most of em are pretty self-explanatory tho.</div>
